        {
            "id": "urn:summary_document_report:quartr.com:2685904:0",
            "title": "STMPA: Q4 2025 returned to year-over-year growth, but FY25 revenues declined 11.1% amid restructuring",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Q4 2025 net revenues grew 0.2% year-over-year to $3.33 billion, with gross margin at 35.2% and a net loss of $30 million due to significant one-time charges. FY25 revenues fell 11.1% to $11.80 billion, while Q1 2026 guidance anticipates $3.04 billion in revenues and a 33.7% gross margin.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Original document: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/accounts/signin?next=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-mediator.tradingview.com%2Fdoc-screener%2Fv1%2Ffiles%2Furn%3Areport%3Aquartr.com%3A2685904-163c9ed8d77ab9fa36d927b7059d40c6\" target=\"_blank\">STMicroelectronics NV [STMPA] Earnings Release — Jan. 29 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-aHOVUrmQ disclaimer-fTXt4Wkx\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-aHOVUrmQ\"><span class=\"heading-aHOVUrmQ\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-aHOVUrmQ link-with-underline-aHOVUrmQ\"><span>This is an AI-generated summary and may contain inaccuracies. Please verify any important information with the original source.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/urn:summary_document_report:quartr.com:2685904:0-stmpa-q4-2025-returned-to-year-over-year-growth-but-fy25-revenues-declined-11-1-amid-restructuring/",
